lead_paragraph: Rickie Fowler made a sparkling start in his bid to rebound from a missed PGA Tour cut last week as he charged into a share of the lead at the weather-disrupted Waste Management Phoenix Open in Arizona on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Fowler in Early Tie for Lead at Phoenix Open
